title: MLB to review Rogers Centre's security following disturbance
text: > Texas MLB to review Rogers Centre's security following disturbance Toronto Blue Jays players celebrate with fans after winning Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Texas Rangers, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Toronto. The Blue Jays clinched their first trip to the American League Championship Series since 1993, overcoming one of the most bizarre plays in playoff history by taking advantage of three Rangers errors for a 6-3 victory. (Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
